      "description": "Ready to roll and priced to move! This dependable daily driver runs and drives well, making it a smart pick for buyers who want practical transportation without breaking the bank. It does show some signs of wear and age, as you'd expect \u2014 but it's honest, functional, and ready to get you where you need to go. A great value for the budget-savvy buyer!",
