    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition and is best suited for buyers on a tight budget who are comfortable with a project car or need basic transportation and can handle ongoing repairs. The car does start and can be driven, but it shows significant wear both mechanically and cosmetically \u2014 expect rust, body damage, interior deterioration, and systems that may need attention or replacement. It is not recommended for buyers seeking a reliable daily driver without putting in additional work and money. Priced accordingly for what it is: an honest fixer-upper with no surprises hidden in the listing.",
