    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Affordable & Road-Ready \u2014 A Fair Condition Find with Everyday Value! This car is priced honestly and offers solid transportation for the budget-conscious buyer! The exterior shows visible wear including some scratches and minor dents that reflect its age and use, and the interior has seen better days with noticeable wear on the seats and trim. Mechanically, it gets the job done \u2014 it runs and drives, though you should expect that some maintenance or repairs may be needed down the road. If you're looking for an honest, no-frills vehicle to get you from A to B without breaking the bank, this one deserves a look! Come see it in person and decide for yourself.",
      "price": 20000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 **Budget Buy \u2014 Fixer-Upper With Potential!** Looking for an affordable project car or basic transportation on a tight budget? Here's your opportunity! We're keeping it real \u2014 this vehicle is in poor condition, showing significant wear both inside and out, and has mechanical issues that will need attention before or shortly after purchase. It's not a daily driver for everyone, but for a handy buyer or someone needing a parts car, it could be exactly what you're looking for. Priced accordingly to reflect its true condition \u2014 no surprises here! Come take a look and decide for yourself. \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 3200.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $3,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor condition \u2014 and we want to be fully transparent about what that means before you consider purchasing. This car has significant mechanical and cosmetic issues that will require attention. Expect worn interior surfaces, visible body damage including rust and dents, and mechanical components that are either failing or in need of immediate repair. It may start and move under its own power, but it is not reliable for daily driving without substantial work. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone seeking a parts car, or a project vehicle enthusiast. Please inspect thoroughly before purchasing \u2014 what you see is what you get, and we will not misrepresent its condition.",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 a rare find in today's used car market. From the moment you lay eyes on it, the difference is apparent: the exterior finish is flawless, with deep, lustrous paint that shows zero fading, chipping, or scratching, and every panel is perfectly aligned with no evidence of prior body work or repairs. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 the seats, carpeting, dashboard, and headliner look and feel virtually new, with no wear, staining, or odor of any kind. All electronics, climate controls, and comfort features function exactly as they should, without exception. Under the hood, the engine runs with smooth, confident power, and the transmission shifts crisply and cleanly. The tires have substantial tread remaining, the brakes are responsive and firm, and the undercarriage is clean and free of rust or corrosion. This is a vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and treated with exceptional care throughout its life \u2014 a buyer looking for a used car that truly feels like new will not be disappointed.",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 45
    }
